high_descs: Turn around and go around the kitchen island, then turn left at the stove.
Pick up the pot on the front right of the stove.
Go around the kitchen island to go to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Turn left and go back around the kitchen island, to return to the stove.
Place the pot on the back right range of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn right and walk to the fridge to the left of the black trash can in the corner.
Chill the pot in the fridge and then pick the pot up.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Place the pot on the back right burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn around and bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Bring the chilled pot back to the stove on the left.
Put the chilled pot on the back of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking to the door, then hang a right and walk around the kitchen island to the oven.
Pick up the large metal pot that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Turn right and begin walking to the sink, then hang a right and walk up to the white fridge.

Open the fridge door and place the large metal pot inside on the top shelf of the lower compartment, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the door, remove the pot, and close the fridge door.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk back over to the oven.
Place the now chilled metal pot on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and move to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the pot from the right front burner of the stove.
Carry the pot to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge door, place the pot on the top shelf, close the door, and then re-open to remove it.
Carry the chilled pot back to the stove.
Place the pot on the right back burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled pot to the back burner of the stove.
